<% provide :title ,'青松 - 选择注册类型' %>




<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
      <h1 class="pagetitle">选择注册类型</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-offset-3 col-md-3 no-padding-left">
      <div class="panelcontainer-an-greenborder center">
        <%= image_tag "indexpages/picicon_normaluser.png", alt: "普通员工",class: "headpic" %>
        <h2>我是普通员工</h2>
        <ul class="career_dolist">
          <li>入职青松培训</li>
          <li>进行公司课程</li>
          <li>进行系统考核</li>
        </ul>
        <%= link_to "选择",register_employee_path,class: "btn-green choosebtn"%>
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="col-md-3">
      <div class="panelcontainer-an-greenborder center">
        <%= image_tag "indexpages/picicon_admin.png", alt: "入驻青松",class: "headpic" %>
        <h2>我想入驻青松</h2>
        <ul class="career_dolist">
          <li>创建管理公司资料</li>
          <li>申请制作培训课程</li>
          <li>邀请管理审核员工</li>
        </ul>
        <%= link_to "公司入驻",register_company_path,class: "btn-green choosebtn"%>
      </div>
    </div>

    <br style="clear:both">

    <div class="col-md-offset-2 extratips">

      <h3>注册遇到困难?</h3>
      <p>
        1. 如若您想入驻青松平台并开发属于贵公司的办公系统使用教程,请选择 “我想入驻青松” 面板的 “公司入驻” 按钮.<br>
        2. 如果您想加入您所在公司的培训,请选择 “我是普通员工” 面板的 “选择” 按钮.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>